# Frontend PWA & Theme

- PWA
  - Manifest at [`frontend/public/manifest.json`](mdc:frontend/public/manifest.json)
  - Service worker at [`frontend/public/service-worker.js`](mdc:frontend/public/service-worker.js)
  - Registered in [`frontend/src/index.tsx`](mdc:frontend/src/index.tsx)
  - Cache strategy: cache-first for shell, network-first for `/api/*`
- Theme
  - Tailwind `darkMode: 'class'`
  - Root toggled via `document.documentElement.classList`
  - Persist preference in `localStorage['theme']` ('dark'|'light')